{"tid":565633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係同ex和平分手但一諗起佢會同現任搞野就會憎佢？","createTime":"2018-02-19T07:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T03:01:05.000Z","uid":129997,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35bbf9bed62c2fe8811d14ae9d3fe2dc4a50280a","tid":565633,"uid":129997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"我個ex係好現實同恨結婚嘅人，而我短期內都唔會考慮結婚。所以就算我地一齊幾開心都好考慮到我地冇將來可言佢最後都係同我分開左。所以當佢同我講佢會同翻佢個ex（有穩定收入）一齊果時雖然我好唔開心但我冇特別憎佢因爲我明白佢個ex比到佢想要嘅野而我唔得。<br />\n咁我地keep住做好朋友啦。但係次次一諗起佢地2個會去旅行一齊訓搞野plan結婚生仔，我就好嬲好想見到佢比條仔飛。<br />\n我想問下我係咪好幼稚定係正常，一方面我想我個ex幸福但另一方面一諗起佢地會有親密接觸我就好憎佢。"},{"pid":"76ef80cb63ff744557892b105744b271d5fa5e7d","tid":565633,"uid":109152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"放低佢啦師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e550aaaad881320177989a956be909245ee4f9a","tid":565633,"uid":172251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:12:05.000Z","msg":"Same here bro"},{"pid":"7ee86905611d99b3525f90fc1c829c24c1077ae1","tid":565633,"uid":84355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"我會好爽，食我口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972040bb41c80a3695e017565741c7b191d6d2b7","tid":565633,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b825ebb86b1ad8ab2697e99ce50eb452ab8fd5","tid":565633,"uid":129997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:47:42.000Z","msg":"我應該真係有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b239f4c076015618e3b5b60eb017e125b6d25eed","tid":565633,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:59:28.000Z","msg":"你未放低"},{"pid":"101609b5